
Ranger Help for: enemy golem
============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing golem means your Ranger is trained to fight constructed bodies:
stone guardians, clay servants, animated statues, and other artificial
creatures.

This is a rare and specialized choice. It is less about animal lore and
more about knowing where joints, cores, seams, and bindings fail.

COMMAND:
  setenemy golem

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
